Manchester United  was drawn to play
Real Madrid in the Champions League round of 16. Barcelona will
face AC Milan and Bayern Munich takes on Arsenal.  The televised draw was made in Nyon, Switzerland where
European soccer ruling body UEFA is based.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
